title: Cyber Watch Face 360
summary: An enhanced time telling experience with this cyber themed watch face.
description: Experience the advanced and technical nature of this cool watch face.  Cyber watchface 360 will have you telling the time in an immersed state.Features include:-choice between 12 hour and 24 hour clock modes- millions of colors available-choice of color for the the theme of the watch face-full date in the MM/DD/YYYY format-advanced minute counter around the watchface-two blinking lights to indicate seconds-cybernetic lights give this watch face a tech feelThis app was designed using the Moto 360 and the Sony 3 but will work on most devices.Visit http://osthoro.wix.com/osthoro for all available watchfaces!
descriptionHTML:
Experience the advanced and technical nature of this cool watch face. Cyber watchface 360 will have you telling the time in an immersed state.

Features include:
-choice between 12 hour and 24 hour clock modes
- millions of colors available
-choice of color for the the theme of the watch face
-full date in the MM/DD/YYYY format
-advanced minute counter around the watchface
-two blinking lights to indicate seconds
-cybernetic lights give this watch face a tech feel

This app was designed using the Moto 360 and the Sony 3 but will work on most devices.

Visit http://osthoro.wix.com/osthoro for all available watchfaces!
